,"starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}],"milestone":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/milestones/12","html_url":"https://github.com/glfw/glfw/milestone/12","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/milestones/12/labels","id":1586124,"node_id":"MDk6TWlsZXN0b25lMTU4NjEyNA==","number":12,"title":"3.3","description":"","creator":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/elmindreda","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"open_issues":0,"closed_issues":266,"state":"closed","created_at":"2016-02-16T16:04:47Z","updated_at":"2019-07-21T23:55:22Z","due_on":null,"closed_at":"2019-04-16T00:42:23Z"},"comments":1,"created_at":"2018-05-27T07:50:15Z","updated_at":"2018-05-28T15:42:14Z","closed_at":"2018-05-28T15:41:26Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Hi, I'm working on a multi-lib cross-platform app, using the Vulkan API and cmake.\r\nI'm using a recent version of CMake, which delivers a FindVulkan module. \r\nGLFW is included as a git submodule and is built as part of my CMake project structure.\r\nCertain libraries in my project structures also depend on the FindVulkan module (which ones don't reference the GLFW library). Only there I refer to the CMake delivery.\r\n\r\nOn Mac, i'm finding the glfw version conflicts with the standard version as the find_library and find_path calls explicitly refer to macOS subdirectory:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    find_library(VULKAN_LIBRARY vulkan.1 HINTS\r\n        \"$ENV{VULKAN_SDK}/macOS/lib\")\r\n    find_path(VULKAN_INCLUDE_DIR NAMES vulkan/vulkan.h HINTS\r\n        \"$ENV{VULKAN_SDK}/macOS/include\")\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf you compare it to the Cmake delivery, it doesn't have this exception code.\r\nThe [LunarG documentation](https://vulkan.lunarg.com/doc/sdk/1.1.73.0/mac/getting_started.html) for the Mac API (see section Command Line) also includes the macOS folder in the VULKAN_SDK environment variable. \r\nThis way the FindVulkan (GLFW version or CMake version) is still matching the documentation.\r\n\r\nAn example of how the environment variables are then set:\r\n> export VULKAN_SDK=\"/Users/<username>/Development/libs/vulkansdk-macos-1.1.73.0/macOS\"\r\n> export DYLD_LIBRARY_PATH=\"$VULKAN_SDK/lib\"\r\n> export VK_LAYER_PATH=\"$VULKAN_SDK/etc/vulkan/explicit_layers.d\"\r\n> export VK_ICD_FILENAMES=\"$VULKAN_SDK/etc/vulkan/icd.d/MoltenVK_icd.json\"\r\n> export PATH=\"$VULKAN_SDK/bin:/opt/local/bin:/opt/local/sbin:$PATH\"\r\n\r\nThe CMake version of the module can be found on their [official git repo](https://github.com/Kitware/CMake/blob/master/Modules/FindVulkan.cmake)\r\n\r\nI'm running:\r\nMacOS: 10.13.2 (High Sierra)\r\nVisual Studio Code\r\nCMake version 3.10.1\r\n\r\nThanks!\r\nRgds,\r\nThomas","closed_by":{"login":"elmindreda","id":133714,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEzMzcxNA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/133714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda","html_url":"https://github.com/elmindreda","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/elmindreda/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/1278/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/glfw/glfw/issues/1278/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}